Who We Are

Jeremy White

Ruben has a background in industrial electronics that he used to launch an engineering firm early in his career. Later he worked at private and publicly traded companies. Ruben has always been fascinated by new technologies and how they can impact people’s lives for the better with practical and affordable solutions.

Kristen White

Kristen is a BSN graduate of Texas Woman’s University and has 20+ years of experience working in the health care field. She has worked with patients of all ages and disease states both in and out of the hospital setting. Over the last 10 years, Kristen’s passion and specialty have moved away from only sick management to life optimization and health maintenance throughout the life span. We can maintain health, prevent disease and grow old gracefully!
